    About Dr. Fatima Tuz Zahra

    I am a dermatologist and Dermatosurgeon from at St. Johns Medical College Hospital, Bengaluru. Previously I worked as Senior Resident of Dermatology at Jawaharlal Nehru Medical College and Hospital, Aligarh Muslim University, Aligarh, India .

    Education

    • Fellowship in Dermatosurgery, St. Johns Medical College Hospital, Bengaluru

      • ​Vitiligo surgeries, Scar revision surgeries, Cyst excisions

      • Ear lobe repair, Nail and hair procedures

      • LASERS and Injectables

    • Senior Resident, Department of Dermatology, JNMCH, AMU, Aligarh
